OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,6,Falthough there will be a fair amount
OL,7,Fof cloud around at times. A few bright
OL,8,For sunny intervals possible, more
OL,9,Fespecially across western Tayside.
OL,10,FCool in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry
OL,13,Falthough rather cloudy. Then the rest
OL,14,Fof the night will be dry with variable
OL,15,Famounts of cloud and clear periods.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,18,Fday with plenty of sunshine, although
OL,19,Flow cloud may linger across eastern
OL,20,FAngus. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
