OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA few
OL,6,Fearly showers on Friday otherwise dry
OL,7,Fbut rather cloudy. Outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fspreading east on Saturday. A few
OL,9,Fshowers in the west Sunday, otherwise
OL,10,Fmainly dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
